1. *Rukom* ga je potrgao. (He ripped it with his hand.) 
2. On je u času izvukao *rukom* nož. (He pulled out a knife in a flash with his hand.)
3. *Rukom* mu je pokazala na vrata. (She pointed to the door with her hand.)
4. On je držao knjigu *rukom*. (He held the book with his hand.)
5. *Rukom* je pokazala da je završila. (She indicated with her hand that she had finished.)
6. On je *rukom* prekinuo borbu. (He stopped the fight with his hand.)